430
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:08,200
Kau tunggu bersamaku
sampai mereka kembali.

431
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:17,000
Raja memberi perintah langsung

432
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,550
kepada pejabat
Menteri Keuangan, Li Xuan,

433
00:23:18,550 --> 00:23:19,790
